deprecation.message:
1.0.0-preview1 and 1.0.0-preview2 of the Windows App SDK contain a critical bug that corrupts your system’s PATH variable. We are fixing this in an upcoming 1.0.0-preview3 release. If you’ve already installed one of these previews, see this GitHub thread for how to resolve the issue: https://github.com/microsoft/WindowsAppSDK/issues/1599

Until Preview 3 is available, we recommend using 1.0.0-experimental1 or being aware of this issue and how it might impact your work.
